            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "A lady whom I know worked at this place they pay on paper 21,000-00 and you need to deposit cash as Rs.11,500-00 in school.  They doing this so that Maharashtra eduction grant are recieved on 21,000-00. This is theft. School ask the same teacher to teach kids Moral Science. They ask parent to pay some part of fees through maternal uncle account as there is a limit in charges to collected when Maharashtra government funds such schools. They take original certificate from teacher so that teacher don't speak about this outside. This we could write as teacher has resigned from that place.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
